info.abstract:
[Behaviour]
Returns an array in which the 'i'-th element is the difference between the 'i'-th and 'i-1'-th element of input array.

[Parameters]
- input measure type : Ophidia typing. Supported types are:
					'oph_double';
					'oph_float';
					'oph_long';
					'oph_int';
					'oph_short';
					'oph_byte'.
- output measure type : Ophidia typing. Supported types are:
					'oph_double';
					'oph_float';
					'oph_int';
					'oph_short';
					'oph_byte'.
- measure : input measure.

[Return type]
Binary-array.

[Examples]
oph_deaccumulate('OPH_DOUBLE','OPH_DOUBLE',measure)
